  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(145, 145, 145);white-space:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 14px;margin:13px 0px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">整理 | 华卫</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">即使你对生成式 AI 模型的内部运作了解不多，也大概率知道它们极其吃内存。正因如此，如今想买一根普通内存条都免不了被狠狠加价。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">最近，谷歌研究院发布了 TurboQuant 压缩算法，能够在提升运行速度并保持准确性不变的前提下，降低大语言模型（LLM）的内存占用。如果 TurboQuant 成功落地，可将 AI 运行时的 “工作内存”，也就是键值缓存（KV cache）压缩至少 6 倍，并在 H100 显卡上实现最高 8 倍的速度提升，从而大幅降低 AI 运行成本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">Cloudflare 的 CEO Matthew Prince 等人甚至称，这是谷歌的 “DeepSeek 时刻”。此前，中国 AI 模型 DeepSeek 实现这样的效率飞跃：该模型在性能保持竞争力的情况下，训练成本仅为对手的零头，且使用的芯片性能较差。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100176203\" data-ratio=\"1.04149377593361\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"964\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=53f832cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5TS1781sic1gHTFJJ7IzbBEyicZzUTHNX1UlHZYSicOCqTeyibiapStXibibes3B5IBiahibMFjSeicWj0yqsFofINAH8ukRYqy8HKiaXgpM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">而 TurboQuant 最关键的亮点是：精度零损失。无需微调，无需训练数据。直接接入任意 Transformer 模型，即可让键值缓存压缩至原体积的一小部分，同时输出结果完全一致。如果这一效果能在实际生产环境中成立，将一夜之间改变长上下文推理的成本格局。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，TurboQuant 发布短短数小时内，内存类股票应声下跌：美光科技跌 3%，西部数据跌 4.7%，闪迪跌 5.7%。原因是投资者开始重新估算，AI 行业未来实际需要的物理内存可能会大幅减少。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1620fc8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNhKGhYw5CuxU3sEcTPdPWQffxKfPewTRGDxoVDictKfNtHjV8VAdibHeKPzPvjialTm3NUic2YrKzUCZk2jxAHD7qs6u32Ncl89paE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;极致无损压缩 AI 效率，还革新了向量检索 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在博客中，谷歌研究院将这项技术描述为一种在不影响性能的前提下缩减 AI 运行内存的全新方法。研究人员表示，该压缩技术采用一种矢量量化方式，解决 AI 处理中的缓存瓶颈问题，本质上能让 AI 在占用更少空间、保持精度的同时记住更多信息。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">TurboQuant 的优化目标是缩减键值缓存的体积，谷歌将其比作一张 “数字备忘单”，用于存储关键信息，避免重复计算。这张备忘单必不可少，因为正如我们常说的，大语言模型本身并不 “懂” 任何东西，它们只是通过向量模拟出理解的效果，向量会映射分词后文本的语义信息。两个向量相近，就代表它们在概念上相似。高维向量可能包含成百上千个嵌入维度，能够描述图像像素、大型数据集等复杂信息，但同时也会占用大量内存，让键值缓存体积暴涨，成为性能瓶颈。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为了让模型更小、更高效，开发者通常会使用量化技术以更低精度运行模型，缺点则是生成效果会变差，分词预测的质量下降。而谷歌的早期测试结果显示，使用 TurboQuant 后，部分场景下性能提升 8 倍、内存占用减少 6 倍，且精度毫无损失。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100176201\" data-ratio=\"0.44907407407407407\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8f7028c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6TEdSMuzcnt7HOt0bU1FpGhkxOYH190VROdhjBtE8kqgSF7LibsReMox8msiafoueTB74dYJoMBTtCSIHWdYftKHibTN3ddAHxwY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">谷歌表示，他们在 Gemma 和 Mistral 两款开源模型上，用一系列长上下文基准测试了这套新压缩算法。结果显示，TurboQuant 在所有测试中下游任务表现完美，同时将键值缓存内存占用降低 6 倍。该算法无需额外训练，就能将缓存量化至仅 3 比特，可直接应用于现有模型。在英伟达 H100 加速器上，使用 4 比特 TurboQuant 计算注意力分数，速度比 32 比特未量化键值快 8 倍。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100176202\" data-ratio=\"0.5796296296296296\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3fe32ad5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm7YCAj84ArjDZaQicwnH4w0ibicDqw2yqicdjKbs6PlmU8CKa2EGzQyX9vRbYeLjsRQC3arotXPdO3yTfSL25icKkerAzjic3n4rFgmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过值得注意的是，TurboQuant 目前尚未大规模部署，现阶段仍只是实验室层面的突破。如果正式落地，TurboQuant 有望降低 AI 模型的运行成本，减少内存消耗。研发这类技术的公司也可能利用释放出的内存运行更复杂的模型。未来大概率会两种方向并存，而移动端 AI 受益可能最为明显。受限于手机硬件条件，TurboQuant 这类压缩技术可以在不上传数据至云端的前提下，提升本地 AI 的生成质量。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">除大语言模型推理外，TurboQuant 也适用于向量检索场景，在检索增强生成（RAG）与相似度搜索中，高维向量同样面临内存压力。使用 TurboQuant 后，索引构建时间几乎降至零（1536 维向量仅需 0.0013 秒，而乘积量化需 239.75 秒）；在 GloVe 数据集上的召回率也优于乘积量化与 RabbiQ 基准模型。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c9389df&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNh6oH4oiaBDGL7pqiaOOLxWsjj3rALNxUyEJ7tUp1AtFDfV0OntDydd8wJx3Bkext4dPTxdEelMoErOaWUPvKfOaZdZmyLxfnodI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></span><span leaf=\"\">技术逻辑大公开：应用到 AI 模型只需两步 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">将 TurboQuant 应用到 AI 模型分为两个阶段，背后是两项关键技术：量化方法 PolarQuant 以及名为 QJL 的训练与优化方法。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为实现高质量压缩，谷歌设计了一套名为 PolarQuant 的系统，以一种截然不同的思路解决内存开销问题。AI 模型中的向量通常采用标准 XYZ 坐标编码，而 PolarQuant 会将向量转换为笛卡尔坐标系下的极坐标。在这个环形网格中，向量被简化为两项信息：半径（核心数据强度）和方向（数据的语义含义）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">谷歌用一个很形象的现实例子来解释：传统编码就像是 “向东走 3 个街区，再向北走 4 个街区”；而用极坐标则可以简化为 “沿 37 度方向走 5 个街区”。这样不仅占用空间更少，还省去了系统开销巨大的数据归一化步骤。PolarQuant 承担了主要的压缩工作，尽管效果显著，但会产生残留误差。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二步则用于修复瑕疵。对此，谷歌提出用量化约翰逊 - 林登斯特劳斯变换（QJL）进行平滑处理，在压缩复杂高维数据的同时，保留数据点之间关键的距离与关联信息。该技术会为模型添加一层 1 比特误差校正层，将每个向量压缩至单个比特（+1 或 - 1），本质上构建了一套高速简写形式，且不会产生任何内存开销。同时为保证精度，QJL 采用一种特殊估算器，对高精度查询与低精度简化数据进行合理平衡，使模型能够精准计算注意力分数，这也是神经网络判断数据重要性的核心机制。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">二者组合起来的效果就是，PolarQuant 实现极致压缩，QJL 以近乎可忽略的成本修正误差。据悉，谷歌计划在下个月的 ICLR 2026 会议上展示他们的研究成果，并展示这两种优化方法。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f1fa4475&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNia94e4iaoyVjbHicUMLqQtVxWf83icibKribzLzPlmGichib48LuozZxALhLg3nJBfE4ZkNibHbjOLGtkIDNmDHiaSwZ7icKmclHqJqvvljg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></span><span leaf=\"\">代码未公布，开发者单靠论文复现可用版 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">尽管谷歌尚未发布任何官方代码或集成库，独立开发者们已经仅凭论文就开始构建可运行的实现版本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">有开发者在 PyTorch 中自定义了 Triton 内核，在 RTX 4090 显卡上对 Gemma 3 4B 模型进行测试，结果显示：在 2 比特精度下，模型输出与未压缩基准版逐字符完全一致。仅用 2 比特存储每个数值，量化后的模型就能与全精度版本实现逐字节完全相同的回复，这表明 TurboQuant 的理论保证在较小模型上切实有效。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">另有开发者通过 MLX 框架在苹果芯片上运行 35B 参数模型并搭载 TurboQuant，在各量化等级下的 “大海捞针” 测试中均取得 6 项满分。在 llama.cpp 社区，已有三名开发者着手开发 C 语言与 CUDA 版本，其中一人表示 18 项测试全部通过，压缩比也与论文数据完全吻合。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">一项研究论文在官方发布前就以如此速度被广泛复现，实属罕见。覆盖 Triton、MLX、llama.cpp 等平台的实现案例，既体现了 TurboQuant 数学设计的清晰性，也反映出 KV 缓存优化作为部署瓶颈的迫切需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过，复现该算法并非易事。一名早期开发者表示，QJL 误差校正模块很难准确实现，简单粗暴的实现方式只会输出乱码。如果不能正确实现 QJL 对内积估算的偏差校正，量化误差会不断累积，导致输出结果完全不可用。目前谷歌仍未发布 TurboQuant 官方代码，vLLM、llama.cpp、Ollama 等主流推理框架也均未集成该技术。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=94e31bb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNhGXj9jBGXWrdR9K7YI2jXiajxCLqYSmfib4ZINjEH1QLhxk9Xp9nBNqCRxXyrJQqJV2bxNY0Ye7IKibrDSUiaUiciaRJzCB6lk6wWR0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">4</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;内存股全跌了，英伟达也在推同款算法 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">市场反应十分迅速。内存类股票纷纷下跌，美光科技股价下跌 3%，西部数据下跌 4.7%，闪迪下跌 5.7%。A 股市场存储芯片股也集体下挫，其中，兆易创新、佰维存储、恒烁股份跌超 5%，江波龙、朗科科技、北京君正、太极实业、中电港跌超 4%，普冉股份、同有科技、万润科技、科翔股份、精智达、云汉芯城、联芸科技跌超 3%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">而在多位分析师看来，这种波动有些反应过度。富国银行分析师 Andrew Rocha 指出，TurboQuant 直接冲击了 AI 系统的内存成本曲线。他表示，如果该技术被广泛采用，很快就会引发一个问题：整个行业实际需要的内存容量究竟有多大。但 Rocha 与其他分析师也同时提醒，AI 内存的需求整体依然强劲，而且压缩算法已存在多年，并未从根本上改变硬件采购规模。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过，市场的担忧并非毫无根据。AI 基础设施支出正以惊人速度增长：仅 Meta 一家，近期就与 Nebius 达成协议，投入高达 270 亿美元用于专属算力；谷歌、微软、亚马逊也共同计划在 2026 年前投入数千亿美元用于数据中心资本支出。一项能将内存需求降低 6 倍的技术，并不会让支出同步减少 6 倍，因为内存只是数据中心成本的一部分。但它会改变成本结构比例，而在如此大规模的投入下，即便只是小幅效率提升，带来的影响也会快速放大。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">TurboQuant 并非唯一一篇将在 ICLR 2026 发表的 KV 缓存压缩方法。据了解，英伟达推出的 KVTC 可实现 20 倍压缩，且精度损失不到 1 个百分点。该算法在 15 亿至 700 亿参数的模型上完成了测试，覆盖范围比 TurboQuant 约 80 亿参数上限的基准测试更广。KVTC 采用了截然不同的底层思路，使用基于主成分分析（PCA）的去相关方法与熵编码，部分思路借鉴自 JPEG 压缩。与 TurboQuant 与数据无关的设计不同，KVTC 需要针对每个模型执行一次性校准步骤，离线计算 PCA 对齐矩阵。作为回报，它在 8000 token 的长提示词下，可将首 token 延迟最高降低 8 倍：在 H100 上从约 3 秒缩短至 380 毫秒。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">英伟达研究员 Adrian Lancucki 表示，“高效的 KV 缓存管理正变得至关重要，闲置缓存必须迅速从 GPU 显存移出，为其他用户腾出空间，并在对话恢复时快速加载。这些基础设施成本如今已体现在商用定价中，例如‘提示词缓存’，并会收取额外费用。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">两种相互竞争的压缩标准在同一场会议同期亮相，标志着 KV 缓存优化正从纯研究课题，逐渐成熟为生产级基础设施层。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://research.google/blog/turboquant-redefining-ai-efficiency-with-extreme-compression/\" target=\"_blank\">https://research.google/blog/turboquant-redefining-ai-efficiency-with-extreme-compression/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://winbuzzer.com/2026/03/26/googles-turboquant-reduces-ai-llm-cache-memory-xcxwbn/\" target=\"_blank\">https://winbuzzer.com/2026/03/26/googles-turboquant-reduces-ai-llm-cache-memory-xcxwbn/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://thenextweb.com/news/google-turboquant-ai-compression-memory-stocks\" target=\"_blank\">https://thenextweb.com/news/google-turboquant-ai-compression-memory-stocks</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌研究院发布 TurboQuant 算法，通过极坐标量化与 QJL 误差校正实现 KV 缓存 6 倍无损压缩，显著提升 LLM 推理效率并引发行业震荡。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌研究院发布 TurboQuant 算法，通过极坐标量化与 QJL 误差校正实现 KV 缓存 6 倍无损压缩，显著提升 LLM 推理效率并引发行业震荡。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了谷歌研究院最新发布的 TurboQuant 压缩技术。该算法针对大语言模型（LLM）推理中的键值缓存（KV cache）瓶颈，通过 PolarQuant（将向量转换为极坐标）和 QJL（量化约翰逊-林登斯特劳斯变换）两项核心技术，实现了在精度零损失的前提下将内存占用降低 6 倍，并在 H100 显卡上实现最高 8 倍的速度提升。文章指出该技术无需微调或额外训练数据，可直接应用于现有 Transformer 模型。目前全球开发者已在 Triton、MLX 等框架上尝试复现。此外，文章还对比了英伟达同期推出的 KVTC 算法，并分析了该技术对存储芯片市场及 AI 基础设施成本结构的潜在冲击。",
  "mainPoints": [
